#18701
{BLUE}Travelling the road of destiny{blue}~

     You are heading south on what was once a well-
     maintained road.  It is now little more than a
     pair of wagon wheel ruts holding stagnant water
     and a central knoll of corrupted, greenish black
     grass.

     The surrounding countryside is strange, almost
     otherworldly.  The trees have lost most of their
     leaves, or perhaps they never had them.  Mists
     rise from the forest, and the sun seems to have
     lost its warmth.  A definite chill lingers in
     the air.

