#18702
{BLUE}Travelling the road of destiny{blue}~

     The surrounding countryside is strange, almost
     otherworldly.  The trees have lost most of their
     leaves, or perhaps they never had them.  Mists
     rise from the forest, and the sun seems to have
     lost its warmth.  A definite chill lingers in
     the air.

     Suddenly, creatures leap at you from the ground,
     dead trees, the dusty rocks.  They attack you
     nipping with eroded but still sharp teeth.  
     Perhaps they were once squirrels or stoats.
     Their long tails retain a few bristled patches,
     their mangy body hair hangs in sparse clumps
     on their lumpy frames.

