#18717
{RED}Heart of the garden{red}~

     You have found your way into the heart of the garden.
     Strangely, the garden's heart is teeming with flowers,
     shrubs, and vines of every description.  A variety of
     sweet odors perfume the air, some so delicate that they
     pass almost unnoticed, others cloying and overwhelming.
     Tiny bees move about, apparently uninterested in you as
     they go about their labors.

     A sudden movement catches your eye.  Just ahead, through
     a tangle of vines spotted with delicate indigo blossoms,
     you notice the slender silhouette of a beautiful woman.
     The instant that your gaze touches her slendor shadow,
     any thought of leaving this garden vanishes.

