#18730
{WHITE}The study{white}~

     There is little order here.  Chairs sit scattered, left
     where they were when the last user pushed himself away.
     Many books rest on shelves, mixed with ancient accounting
     records and travel journals of Spellseers who journeyed
     abroad.  Among the books a few stand out.  History of the
     Spellseers, Spulzeer and a guide of some sorts regarding
     the undead.

     Suddenly a crash sounds behind you.  In the doorway stands
     a disheveled man with a wild look in his eyes.  His 
     uncombed hair sticks up at odd angles, and he looks as
     if he has slept in his clothes for weeks.  He carries a
     great broadsword that he seems only too willing to use.

     With a wordless scream he charges you, sword raised high.
     Before he reaches you he stops.  He shakes his head in
     bewilderment and begins to mutter something you can not
     quite make out.

~
