#18798
{CY}Shaundakul's Tavern{cy}~

     The tavern is a comfortable, well-appointed roadhouse
     that serves what is reputed to be the best rabbit stew
     in all the lands.  The name of the place is derived from
     the lodestone slab that serves as the counter top for the
     bar.  It is said to have come from a ruined temple of the
     god of caravans.  The food quality here is good, and the
     prices are low enough to appeal to caravan drivers and 
     officers of the guard as well.

